BVP PHYSIOLOGICAL STATE DIAGRAM

A physiological state diagram based on the BVP phase plane will now be de-
scribed. The coordinates x and y are for the moment not to be identified physically
except to say that x shares the properties of both membrane potential and excitabil-
ity, while y is responsible for accommodation and refractoriness. Later, x will be
identified with membrane potential. The parameter z corresponds to stimulating

